Sat Feb  1 16:17:02 UTC 2025 - Andreas Stieger <andreas.stieger@gmx.de>

- Update to version 5.2.1:
  * new file encoding type null_data to read NUL as LF and vice
    versa; supports reading xargs -0 output for example

